'''Lance Dreher''' is a two-time [[Universe Championships|Mr. Universe]] and former [[AAU Mr. America|Mr. America]]. Dreher was born in [[Chicago, Illinois]], on June 27, 1955. Dreher has placed in the top 3 of 10 professional body building championships. One of Lance's greatest body building features is his 23.5 inch biceps. After his last competition in 1992, Lance completed his PhD in Physical Therapy and is a certified life coach. Lance currently hosts a radio talkshow on [[KFYI]] called "Fitness Talk w/ Lance Dreher"<ref>KFYI Talk Radio{{cite web|title=News Talk Radio 550 KFYI|url=http://www.kfyi.com/main.html|work=Radio station homepage|publisher=KFYI|accessdate=19 June 2011}}</ref>
